  "statement": "Discovery is idempotent: no duplicate-entity minting. When discovery encounters a Tenant / Product / Project that is **already minted**, the app SHALL surface the existing entity and SHALL NOT create a duplicate. - *Acceptance:* Running onboarding against an area whose Project is already minted results in **zero** new duplicate entities; the existing entity is reused/surfaced",
